de.cau.lps.debugger.program

Interface Debugger

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DebuggerImpl, DebuggerMock

    public interface Debugger
    This interface must be implemented by any class containing the actual debugging logic.
    Author:
    Thomas Ulrich
